                <h1>Find Wallpaper on iPhone: A Quick Guide</h1>
                <p>To find wallpaper on your iPhone, navigate to the Settings app. Tap on "Wallpaper," where you can view your current wallpaper and choose new ones. You can select from pre-installed images or your own photos. Additionally, you can set different wallpapers for your Lock Screen and Home Screen for a personalized touch.</p>
